1007,Ryan,29,Male,Edmonton,Mouse,Accessories,5,40,2025-01-18
1008,Amanda,41,Female,Calgary,Laptop,Electronics,1,1500,2025-01-19
1009,Chris,33,Male,Medicine Hat,Tablet,Electronics,2,650,2025-01-20
